Assignment 2 Description

-> Question requires:
1) Calculating weights of portfolio with specifications.

2) Drawing an effeciency frontier graph based on Two Fund Separation Theorem by ranging between given
minimum and maximum expected return of a portfolio consists of 4 different assets.

3) Calculating weights of tendency portfolio, using the weights find the portfolio's expected return 
and standard deviation.

4) Drawing a Capital Market Line (CML, the tendency line) in the graph of effeciency frontier.

5) Find the weights of the globally minimum variance portfolio.

6) Solve and find weights of the portfolio by using Lagrange equation, also writing down the associated 
system of linear equations.
